[PRF-001] Profile parse error — The profile JSON/TOML could not be parsed.
Resolution: Validate profile syntax with the profile linter.
---
[PRF-002] Profile schema invalid — The profile does not conform to the expected schema.
Resolution: Compare against the profile JSON schema in docs/reference.
---
[PRF-003] Profile merge conflict — Two profiles define conflicting axis assignments.
Resolution: Resolve overlapping assignments in the more-specific profile.
---
[PRF-004] Profile not found — The specified profile file does not exist.
Resolution: Check the profile path and file name.
